%% F22 - Sequence de scan QR et mise a jour du statut
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor OP as Operateur terrain
    participant APP as Application mobile Flutter
    participant API as API Laravel / ScanController
    participant AUTH as Middleware Sanctum + RBAC
    participant SCAN as ScanService
    participant FLOW as ScanFlowService + ValidationService
    participant DB as Base de donnees

    OP->>APP: Scanner le QR code du camion
    APP->>API: POST /api/scan (qr_code, device_time, device_id)
    API->>AUTH: Verifier token et role
    AUTH-->>API: Utilisateur authentifie
    API->>SCAN: submitScan(qr_code, user, device)
    SCAN->>DB: Rechercher camion par qr_code
    DB-->>SCAN: Camion actif
    SCAN->>FLOW: Determiner action attendue
    FLOW->>DB: Lire scan_flows et trip actif
    DB-->>FLOW: Etape courante et contraintes
    FLOW-->>SCAN: Action valide (START / ARRIVE / LEAVE / RETURN)
    SCAN->>DB: Creer ou mettre a jour Trip
    SCAN->>DB: Enregistrer ScanLog
    DB-->>SCAN: Transaction confirmee
    SCAN-->>API: Resultat avec statut courant
    API-->>APP: 200 OK + message + prochaine etape
    APP-->>OP: Afficher confirmation

    alt Scan invalide
        FLOW-->>SCAN: Action refusee
        SCAN-->>API: Erreur metier
        API-->>APP: 4xx + message explicite
        APP-->>OP: Afficher erreur
    end
